    "client_msg_id": "18a51adf-776c-4eed-a635-033b3fe841e6",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "What I've seen working in practice is explicit \"top of the week\", \"top of the year\", etc lists based on voting. I don't think you'll be able to usefully fit both new items and old good ones in the same \"front page\", but if you relax that requirement it gets easier.",
